    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It runs beautifully and has been really well-loved, so it's in great shape for its next adventure. If you're looking for something reliable that still feels fresh and fun to drive, this is the one! I'm sad to see it go, but I'd love for it to head to a good home. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
