    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2008 Porsche Cayman S. This mid-engine platform utilizes the M97.21 3.4L flat-six engine with VarioCam Plus, delivering linear power through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The suspension geometry remains tight, offering the high-fidelity steering feedback these chassis are known for. Recent preventative maintenance includes a cooling system refresh and a comprehensive Bore Scoring inspection (negative). While showing minor cosmetic patina expected of a 'good' condition driver, the powertrain remains robust with no vacuum leaks or IMS issues. Equipped with 4-piston monobloc calipers and cross-drilled rotors for consistent thermal management during spirited driving.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
