      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and comfort. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish with only minor road chips consistent with careful use and typical highway driving. Inside, you'll find a strictly smoke-free cabin featuring premium upholstery in excellent shape, with all power features, dual-zone climate control, and the infotainment system functioning flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is robust; it has been serviced at regular intervals, providing a smooth, responsive drive with plenty of life left in the tires and brakes. We have recently performed a full fluid flush and a multi-point inspection to ensure it is road-ready. This is a reliable, turn-key option for anyone seeking a high-quality daily driver that has been treated with respect. Full service records are available for your review.",
      "price": 34500.0,
